org.apromore.plugin.property

Class PluginPropertyType<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apromore.plugin.property.PluginPropertyType<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of Property
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyType<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RequestPropertyType

    public class PluginPropertyType<T>
extends Object
implements PropertyType<T>
    PropertyType used by a Plugin defining its properties (e.g. parameters). It takes care of allowing values of specified Class only. Also two Properties are considered 'equal' if their 'id' is the same.
    Author:
    Felix Mannhardt (Bonn-Rhein-Sieg University oAS)
